latestIgtvVideos.title: In Frame we have:- popeye ki favourite chaat😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So I recently visited this restaurant @masaledaarthane . I had no idea that the Palak Chaat I had ordered would be so delicious. The chef used nitrogen to cut the chaat into little chunks, and because it was so cold, he added green chutney, sweet curd, tamarind chutney, and chaat masala to add flavour, then decorated it with sev and pomegranate and boom, our cold wonderful chaat was ready to eat. If you ever visit this place, it’s a must have!!
.
.
.
